{"about_the_game":"Horoscopicus is a game inspired by 2D platformers from a certain incredibly well known portable console from the 90s!<br>Play as <strong>Horo</strong> in this 2D Retro platformer and try your best to collect the 12 zodiac signs (<i>AND PET THE SECRET ANIMALS</i>) so that you may unlock the door to the mysterious 13th zodiac!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798670/extras/PetTheCat.gif?t=1666458692\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798670/extras/features.png?t=1666458692\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore 12 levels + Special versions, all inspired by their own unique zodiac sign!<br></li><li> Choose your own path! The initial 12 levels can be played in any order!<br></li><li> 4 Different upgrade types which change character visuals to match!<br></li><li> Find and <strong>PET 12 DIFFERENT SECRET ANIMALS!</strong> :D<br></li><li> Several selectable screen borders! (Can you find out how to change them?)<br></li><li> Lots of references to other games and media! <br></li><li> Simple controls! (A Jump button, an Attack button and directional keys for Movement.)<br></li><li> An assist/accessibility mode that can help with those particularly tough sections!<br></li><li> An amazingly unique soundtrack made by TheLuzical!<br></li><li> One difficulty, tailored to be the intended experience!<br></li><li> Speedrun friendly! (Enemies behave under cycles)<br></li><li> Total length of the game should be around 3h~, though it highly depends from player to player! :)</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798670/extras/soundtrack.png?t=1666458692\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798670/extras/Album_Cover.png?t=1666458692\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Disclaimer:</h2>This is my first big game and it was completed <i>mostly</i> as a solo project.<br>While I got some help during development, expect a more &quot;traditional indie&quot; quality to the game! :)<br>Nonetheless, I hope you manage to enjoy it regardless!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Capricorn!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798670/31f792cda7e9669de04832f187eb426c2b2a0f26.jpg"},{"name":"Taurus!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798670/3e8b84cdd38067777cf3e52ea9d6ebb87110a517.jpg"},{"name":"Virgo!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798670/eac2847721f9106ad3736fff4dd425f3b617022f.jpg"},{"name":"Aquarius!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798670/86ed9c3bce38a6dbcb9f82d1ba6179f563271f5e.jpg"},{"name":"Gemini!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798670/74ee9ff0c1a49bec616e21839524eca40b52558a.jpg"},{"name":"Libra!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798670/db62bf66a5eef0c51041df9deec95374a450871f.jpg"},{"name":"Pisces!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798670/027672922bf5331f54a90f5bc81ff9962f862a0c.jpg"},{"name":"Cancer!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798670/490278e0b511ca11290618b873d18e827b449aa1.jpg"},{"name":"Scorpio!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798670/0d2f47bff9129dbb350230c63f114bfb38ebf33f.jpg"},{"name":"Aries!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1798670/b574e50929f8596146ce5b1c243889ec75c7b890.jpg"}],"total":28},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1798670/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1666458692","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/17